    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 57-62-9, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO ALLOW CERTAIN QUALIFIED BUSINESSES OR INDUSTRIES TO RECEIVE INCENTIVE PAYMENTS UNDER THE MISSISSIPPI ADVANTAGE JOBS ACT FOR 10 YEARS UNDER CERTAIN CONDITIONS; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 57-62-13, 57-114-5, 57-114-7 AND 57-114-9, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, FOR THE PURPOSE OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
